latestIgtvVideos.title: SKINCARE HACKS ✨🧡
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Hey guys! My love for skincare and finding tips to maximise its use is never-ending. And that is exactly what happened with my FOREO UFO now that I've been using it for a long time. 

Check out the video where I share some amazing ideas on how I’ve been using the Foreo UFO Make My Day Mask for the past few weeks while exploring DIY at home.

1: Use the leftover essence in the UFO mask sachet for multiple uses, or for other parts of my body like my neck or hands. It brings an even tone to the body too.

2: Use 1 UFO mask multiple times by just turning the other side and running it through the water. Yes, you may re-use it and the result is as good as the first time.

I hope you find this video helpful and do share your skincare hacks in the comments below. @foreo_in 

https://foreo.se/1khnm

#homeremedies #Beauty #homespaday #selfconfidence #FOREOUFO #skincaretips #selfpampering
